<snippet>
	<content><![CDATA[SetModelScale(${1:float scale})]]></content>
	<tabTrigger>SetModelScale</tabTrigger>
	<scope>source.lua</scope>
<description>Sets the model's scale to <i>scale</i>, <br/>so if a unit had its model scale at 1, and you use <i>SetModelScale(<b>10.0</b>)</i>, it would set the scale to <b>10.0</b>.</description>
</snippet>